				<td colspan="2"><span>Well i talked to a couple of people about this.
<br />

<br />
Here is what they have come up with.
<br />

<br />
1. First if you are duel boxing with the router (and you not using a file share program) you should not have bandwith probelms at least not from the game. This game can be used with a dial up modem.
<br />

<br />
2. I hooked up my modem directly to my computer and the same thing happened. (so my router is fine Good News, Bad News is my ISP is messing up) So that could be worse.
<br />

<br />
3. IF you have any problems make sure all the ports are open. eq uses something like ports 1225 threw 100000 or something like that.</span></td>
